<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include("partials/head", { title: "Monster Energy", css: "/css/style.css" }) %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("partials/header") %>
    <div id="loader">
      <img src="/images/monsterlogo.svg" alt="Monster Logo" />
    </div>
    <div class="main" id="Start">
      <div class="banner">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-12 banner-up">
            <div class="p-4">
              <p>
                The white can of Monster is more than just an energy drink — it’s a symbol. A reflection of snow-capped
                mountains standing silent against the sky, untouched and eternal. It carries the idea of purity, but not
                weakness; silence, but not emptiness.
                <br />

                When you crack open a White Monster, it’s like standing at the summit at dawn. The air is thin, cold,
                and alive with potential. The horizon stretches infinitely, and in that endless view, you realize:
                energy isn’t just something you consume, it’s something you awaken.
                <br />

                Monster Ultra White is not about sweetness or indulgence. It’s about clarity. It’s about chasing the
                sharp edge of life, where every decision is raw and every step feels like it cuts into the fabric of
                reality. Like the mountain itself, it challenges you — to climb higher, to push further, to embrace the
                silence and transform it into motion.
                <br />

                In the heart of the white peaks, nothing is given. Everything is earned. And White Monster is a reminder
                of that truth: the energy you need is already inside you. This is not sugar, not distraction, but pure
                drive — as crisp and unstoppable as the wind carving its path across the mountain.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-12 banner-down">
            <div id="monsterCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
              <div class="carousel-inner">
                <% images.filter(img => img.section.toLowerCase() === "carousel").forEach((img, index) => { %>
                <div class="carousel-item <%= index === 0 ? 'active' : '' %>">
                  <div class="carousel-img-container">
                    <img src="<%= img.url %>" class="carousel-img" alt="<%= img.alt_text %>" />
                  </div>
                </div>
                <% }) %>
              </div>

              <button
                class="carousel-control-prev"
                type="button"
                data-bs-target="#monsterCarousel"
                data-bs-slide="prev"
              >
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
              </button>
              <button
                class="carousel-control-next"
                type="button"
                data-bs-target="#monsterCarousel"
                data-bs-slide="next"
              >
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about" id="About">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-8">
              <div class="bubble">
                <p>
                  Founded in 2002, Monster Energy is a global leader in the energy drink industry. Headquartered in
                  Corona, California, Monster quickly grew to become one of the most recognized and influential brands
                  in the world of beverages.
                  <br />
                  Monster Energy is dedicated to producing high-quality energy drinks that fuel people’s passions,
                  whether it’s sports, music, gaming, or everyday challenges. Known for its bold flavors, innovative
                  products, and distinctive branding, Monster has created a community of fans who embrace an active and
                  adventurous lifestyle.
                  <br />
                  Beyond drinks, Monster Energy is heavily involved in sports and cultural events, sponsoring extreme
                  sports, motorsports, and music festivals worldwide. The brand’s mission is simple: to energize people
                  to push their limits, live boldly, and embrace life without compromise.
                  <br />
                  With White Monster and other products in its portfolio, Monster continues to innovate, offering
                  options that cater to different tastes and lifestyles while staying true to the core values of energy,
                  performance, and excitement.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-section" id="Gallery">
        <div class="container">
          <h1>Gallery</h1>

          <div class="gallery">
            <% images .filter(img => img.section.toLowerCase() === "gallery") .forEach((img) => { %>
            <figure>
              <a href="<%= img.url %>" data-toggle="lightbox" data-gallery="gallery">
                <img src="<%= img.url %>" alt="<%= img.alt_text %>" />
              </a>
            </figure>
            <% }) %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="products" id="Products">
        <div class="container">
          <h1>Our Products</h1>
          <div class="row">
            <% products.forEach((product) => { %>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
              <div class="card">
                <a href="/product/<%= product.id %>">
                  <img src="<%= product.url %>" class="card-img-top" alt="<%= product.alt_text %>" />
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title"><%= product.name %></h2>
                    <p class="card-text"><%= product.description %></p>
                    <p class="card-price"><%= product.price %> Kč</p>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <% }) %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="news" id="Events">
        <div class="container">
          <h1>Latest Events</h1>
          <div class="rect">
            <% news .sort((a, b) => new Date(b.date) - new Date(a.date)) .slice(0, 3) .forEach((event) => { %>
            <a href="/event/<%= event.id %>">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 imgNews">
                  <img src="<%= event.url %>" alt="<%= event.alt_text %>" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 content">
                  <p class="tags"><%= event.tags %></p>
                  <h3 class="title"><%= event.title %></h3>
                  <p class="text"><%= event.content %></p>
                  <p class="date"><%= event.date.toISOString().slice(0, 10) %></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </a>
            <% }) %>
          </div>
          <div class="butt">
            <button class="butt" data-href="/events">All Events</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/javascript.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/index.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/loader.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bs5-lightbox@1.8.5/dist/index.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
